{"tid":2354470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國特色：辦完喪事辦床事、悲傷不忘性趣","createTime":"2021-01-05T13:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T14:00:00.000Z","uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"45f4f233c7954ce9b3c398a376e0007c0ce39e38","tid":2354470,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:16:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">武漢殯葬業總是兼賣情趣用品？ 奇特店面內幕曝光</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/01/05/phpn9WdFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F01%2F05%2Fphpn9WdFV.jpg&h=b3acdd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國武漢經常發現喪葬用品與情趣用品在同一家店裡販售，為當地街頭的特殊景象。（圖擷自微信公眾號「公路商店」）<br />\n<br />\n2021/01/05 17:30<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">中國武漢經常發現喪葬用品與情趣用品在同一家店裡販售</span>，許多第一次看到的民眾都覺得不可思議，不過當地人都習以為常，而原因其實就是為了節省租金成本，<span class=\"red\">在一家店鋪中滿足武漢人從早到晚、從生到死的各種需求。</span><br />\n<br />\n微信公眾號「公路商店」4日刊出一篇文章表示，一走進武漢街頭，經常可以看到販售喪葬用品的「花圈店」與情趣用品的「性保健店」在同一店面，令許多初到武漢的民眾產生深刻印象，不過這樣的原因其實很單純，根據當地習俗，若家中有人去世，最好在清晨訂好花圈，以利上午出殯火化，「花圈店」也都開在社區樓下，另家中有變故的民眾能第一時間處理後事。<br />\n<br />\n而在早期網路購物不發達的情況下，<span class=\"red\">許多人為了解決生理需求都直接去店面購買情趣用品，「花圈店」設店在住宅區附近，加上又是24小時營業，許多老闆在店裡做起了其他生意，供應情趣用品給需要的民眾</span>，而形成這樣奇特的店面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/01/05/phpwczKTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F01%2F05%2FphpwczKTg.jpg&h=6e7d608e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「花圈店」設店在住宅區附近，加上又是24小時營業，許多老闆在店裡做起了其他生意，供應情趣用品給需要的民眾，而形成這樣奇特的店面。（圖擷自微信公眾號「公路商店」）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3402000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3402000&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=b2a855f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3402000&h=232c1e97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3402000</a>"},{"pid":"bdb429b5693d79e91c3faa8aa18cdb292c1db315","tid":2354470,"uid":61005,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:17:35.000Z","msg":"拜完山屌個閪出一出污氣"},{"pid":"0a519a020cdbc95c7fd99f8f899ac6340b31add6","tid":2354470,"uid":40272,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"同條屍講 起身屌閪啦"},{"pid":"4a1795287e5e28c1e6f32963981294f84acda515","tid":2354470,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.meituan.net/mogu/ddf6bbe1bfc7ed55dceb278e782d2ccd895855.jpg%40300w_225h_1e_1c_1l%7Cwatermark%3D1%26%26r%3D1%26p%3D9%26x%3D2%26y%3D2%26relative%3D1%26o%3D20\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.meituan.net%2Fmogu%2Fddf6bbe1bfc7ed55dceb278e782d2ccd895855.jpg%2540300w_225h_1e_1c_1l%257Cwatermark%253D1%2526%2526r%253D1%2526p%253D9%2526x%253D2%2526y%253D2%2526relative%253D1%2526o%253D20&h=a624c7e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5cc090281b08d8c2930fa1666ed7a0123521f6ae","tid":2354470,"uid":313848,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:20:12.000Z","msg":"好明顯左面賣性用品,右面賣cosplay壽衣"},{"pid":"cce2fe8a868ebdb410af301e4d68ac01b4c1d84d","tid":2354470,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BXwua9t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBXwua9t.jpg&h=edea73ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做生意個門面咁肉酸，好似垃圾房咁，買乜都冇信心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312481d6fc8c0167b21401e29869dbf4f3a3c7c7","tid":2354470,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=38s0apa/39n800010oq95o80pq18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail